/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1af18f1d75d772965aff74d143dfbb1ef1e93b","tid":295494,"uid":82103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"上面褪黑激數係幾好，但主要係俾你調節用，唔適合長期。<br />\n<br />\n我建議你試下臨瞓前做啲對瞓教有幫助嘅活動，好似飲杯牛奶/威士忌/睇書/做運動等等，你可以試下邊種適合你再養成一個睡前習慣，開始有睡意再上床，加強張床同訓教嘅聯繫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd76220c308b06132c5358a7255ae6fa8fcd14c","tid":295494,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:42:25.000Z","msg":"又訓唔著"},{"pid":"0d41344ee9feff83d641f2769c780bb4ebbd24a2","tid":295494,"uid":88025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:44:57.000Z","msg":"唔好諗ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c3e8b4616d2df2858936ed703cad563a557534","tid":295494,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又訓唔著</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9deaff3d163463ece7537e7224606198756fca","tid":295494,"uid":124858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好諗ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求方法"},{"pid":"da002234707b3b86060244e42719780b3d8c585a","tid":295494,"uid":88025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好諗ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求方法</blockquote><br />\n我都失眠緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37810b06d8253b4d6853f98a0adef38afe0bcf41","tid":295494,"uid":39245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:18:20.000Z","msg":"細個暑假做讀書報告， 睇射鵰（小說version）有一幕係馬鈺教郭靖內功， 其中主要係教佢點訓覺， 我個時小學雞on99跟住黎試， 點知又真係幾放鬆<br />\n<br />\n那道人道：「睡覺之前，必須腦中空明澄澈，沒一絲思慮。然後斂身側臥，鼻息綿綿，魂不內蕩，神不外游。」<br />\n<br />\n斂身側臥我就冇跟， 但係&ldquo;魂不內蕩，神不外游&ldquo;其實好難， 當我嘗試唔理出面所有雜聲， 我就會注意咗自己呼吸， 當我唔聽自己呼吸， 又會留意咗出面雜聲， 最後反複可能轉咗5-10次， 先會真正魂不內蕩，神不外游， 好放鬆咁訓著<br />\n<br />\n利申: 雖然1999但係真心冇吹水"},{"pid":"80635580bce410a3e7ae847bb1149b3b445f656c","tid":295494,"uid":8775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b9715e6fee930f7626e9a80dbbd0a49e9709ac3","tid":295494,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"睇史書，傳記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f91220ad8913a4af59157e7675636e30bd2c6a","tid":295494,"uid":42527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"訓唔到就同自己講：我係唔撚訓架啦 <br />\n但照閉目養神 之後就自然訓著左"},{"pid":"ebe6c05ee97ed391daecd92dfba82476f0fb8d94","tid":295494,"uid":4150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T01:50:14.000Z","msg":"同在條女做完愛，沖一沖身，包你訓到死豬咁"},{"pid":"6b1fe05dc1abb0813113accc449c4887c067f0a9","tid":295494,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bed9ca8915dd81760cea8319324b44b5c10834","tid":295494,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"近排發明左個<br />\n<br />\n就係合埋眼聽好靜既歌，但個心就諗住要頂到佢播完先訓，就會好眼訓<br />\n<br />\n反手訓"},{"pid":"9ee5903733f87dadc06b99b121773aa2a7efb4e1","tid":295494,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T20:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排發明左個<br />\n<br />\n就係合埋眼聽好靜既歌，但個心就諗住要頂到佢播完先訓，就會好眼訓<br />\n<br />\n反手訓</blockquote><br />\n反手訓係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856d0dd81c123f6ad06550f4fac7350db7359fb0","tid":295494,"uid":88385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T20:11:33.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"cc0af65743626066a5d7