eplyTime":"2017-06-27T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"失眠三年，食藥都係一時時有用<br />\n如果第二日要返工有緊要嘢做真係唔好食<br />\n個人會處於冇靈魂嘅狀態"},{"pid":"e89d910adc715f2eff62079753a644973c885fd3","tid":295494,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:13:10.000Z","msg":"試下唔好諗任何野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好難"},{"pid":"355eea67109f5228b3a6628660ef49cca8e7ced0","tid":295494,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下唔好諗任何野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好難</blockquote><br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b336daf188316691db522a1d38d26f5a6e772ac8","tid":295494,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"以前玩過爐石<br />\n果陣有上youtube 睇下片抄下牌<br />\n點知 睇睇下訓著左<br />\n一次係咁 兩次都係咁<br />\n比我發現到:哇屌 原來睇人玩爐石好撚易訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此 我就無失眠過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5594b75a8a8963183665b71141b4bf46bcad7ed","tid":295494,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"訓唔著通常HJ2Q<br />\n之後好快就訓左"},{"pid":"28d4129e4bdf1029c0a6e6039f09bf8e8c604df5","tid":295494,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"香港有冇安眠藥買？我見外國一食就即訓咁"},{"pid":"131cfa098c892709bf37355b37b5af0c9ff93d89","tid":295494,"uid":125404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"唔諗著去訓就唔會失眠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7834fe83e6c5a091ea1bd1b109ad9f03e8376d50","tid":295494,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失眠三年，食藥都係一時時有用<br />\n如果第二日要返工有緊要嘢做真係唔好食<br />\n個人會處於冇靈魂嘅狀態</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁<br />\n失眠左3年<br />\n因為壓力太大<br />\n食左藥都冇用<br />\n有時冇訓過 <br />\n通常每日訓3-4個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298ee0613e3d53fb5d53c02f19d263f445a70c6f","tid":295494,"uid":4304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"慣左個人會平訓時慢慢放鬆個身<br />\n每呼一口氣就再放鬆d<br />\n試幾次就會feel到個人慢慢沈落去<br />\n就會好易訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670c9ae6aaad86c62123dbc650fc26a6a58e9364","tid":295494,"uid":107605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失眠三年，食藥都係一時時有用<br />\n如果第二日要返工有緊要嘢做真係唔好食<br />\n個人會處於冇靈魂嘅狀態</blockquote><br />\n咁係你隻藥唔啱嗰個情況<br />\n有啲藥係long acting<br />\n例如睡眠效果有12hrs<br />\n如果你訓9個鐘起身 剩番3個鐘就會hangover 好似前一晚飲醉酒黎既感覺<br />\n所以如果呢啲情況 應該揀啲快速見效 而藥效又比較短時間既藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91313ee42e091377bb9f30d7d1d9cabdefae2bf4","tid":295494,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:59:28.000Z","msg":"各位失眠嘅巴絲 快d瞓喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}